{"tid":361190,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"龘䶛䨻䎱㸞蚮䡶䴞䴝䯬䬛䰕㹚","createTime":"2017-08-16T01:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T16:53:21.000Z","uid":71642,"like":56,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ffb7cce1ef0e0a4daaaff252f10315f8ae68df2","tid":361190,"uid":71642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:44:02.000Z","msg":"於是龘䶛䨻䎱㸞蚮䡶䴞䴝䯬䬛䰕㹚<br />\n砍向㱎䖘䵈䶁䘔䶑䘓鋱䩳䵷㒪䪉䉥<br />\n然後[那個巨龍]㱎䖘䵈䶁䘔䶑䘓鋱䩳䵷㒪䪉䉥<br />\n咬了[那個勇者]龘䶛䨻䎱㸞蚮䡶䴞䴝䯬䬛䰕㹚<br />\n最後龘䶛䨻䎱㸞蚮䡶䴞䴝䯬䬛䰕㹚<br />\n他戰勝了㱎䖘䵈䶁䘔䶑䘓鋱䩳䵷㒪䪉䉥<br />\n救出了公主䥸䝟䳮䟑䎘䫱䉷䰯䕈䟐䬝<br />\n回到了䥰龘䰕㽌䇁䵄䵻䬛蟿䆉㖀城<br />\n國王聽說龘䶛䨻䎱㸞蚮䡶䴞䴝䯬䬛䰕㹚<br />\n他打敗了<br />\n㱎䖘䵈䶁䘔䶑䘓鋱䩳䵷㒪䪉䉥<br />\n就把公主䥸䝟䳮䟑䎘䫱䉷䰯䕈䟐䬝<br />\n嫁給龘䶛䨻䎱㸞蚮䡶䴞䴝䯬䬛䰕㹚<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=Qwosl45YgkU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dyoutu.be%26v%3DQwosl45YgkU&d=%2Fn%2BpqTlSPub4HM7b6wCAsC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=697768ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=Qwosl45YgkU</a>"},{"pid":"3c70c11449a2fbd25d3890ac52010c26750572c0","tid":361190,"uid":19072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T02:53:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aed684038157171f90f4e507bcdce73b69a969a0","tid":361190,"uid":16783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T04:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9af8b8e96c937c0517805b444254f2473661c6","tid":361190,"uid":5532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:01:33.000Z","msg":"以為亂碼"},{"pid":"2c78b3742d7ef6251db352de7768661ab2c51abb","tid":361190,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:06:05.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286a7412a28cb80934959e9a8cb850f10808c2a1","tid":361190,"uid":98209,"like":0,"disl